post.summary: Retrieves availability slots for sales appointments
Books appointment for provided slot key
Retrieves availability slots for sales appointments
Books appointment for provided slot key

slotKey.description: The SlotKey returned from the availability request is used to identify which availability slot to book the appointment for

leadSourceID.description: LeadSourceID will set opportunity lead source to this value

durationMins.description: A value in minutes for the length of the appointment. Will default to 60 if not supplied.

estimatedTravelMins.description: A value in minutes used to calculate utilization of sales reps within the slot. Will default to 20 if not supplied.

latitude.description: Latitude of the appointment location is required to determine the correct timezone to book the appointment in

longitude.description: Longitude of the appointment location is required to determine the correct timezone to book the appointment in

appointmentMinutes.description: Represents the duration of the appointment to be booked in

filterByRoster.description: When set to true only rostered times for each sale rep will be checked for availability, when set to false 9am to 5pm is assumed.

filterBySkills.description: When set to true only reps with the required skills for the products of interest will be considered

productsOfInterests.description: Array of products of interest ids to be used when FilterBySkills is set to true

V1_LiveDiarySalesAvailabilityRequestMode.description: Represents a request model for live diary sales availability.
